We use Microsoft Application Insights (link) for analytics purposes. This service, provided by Microsoft, helps us understand how our services are being used and improve our offerings. The information collected by this service may include your IP address, browser type, operating system, and other usage data. We use this information to enhance our services and provide you with a better user experience. We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.
Legal basis:
The processing is carried out in accordance with Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR on the basis of our legitimate interest in improving the stability and functionality of our website.
Recipients:
Recipients of the data may be technical service providers who act as data processors for the operation and maintenance of our website.
